metadata.name: Pixel Heroes #2
metadata.description: By creating Pixel Heroes using the NEW (ERC5050) smart contract, we are enabling users to have a chance to acquire a FREE mint during our dual NFT mint cycle. With 3,000 stock in total, there will be a 2 to 1 chance at receiving a FREE mint. Pixel Heroes can be minted at pixelheroesnft.com with a 0.005 gamble mint, 50% chance at a guaranteed FREE mint. No Discord or roadmap cause we're not pussies.
